  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5069580">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5069580/" class="title-link">关于《安静的位置》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5069580"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/46014232/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u46014232-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/46014232/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Alexandra</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-08-20"
      class="main-meta">2011-08-20 00:06:30</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5069580_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   老实说，读完此书略有些失望心情。 对周国平有份特殊的情愫，在曾经迷茫徘徊孤单的青春岁月里，有他共鸣、指引、慰藉，才度过了一段难熬的时光。想起高中时，每个夜晚读完一段周国平先生的随笔杂文，听着小夜曲在园中散步，总是平静而充实，满心的安然和坚定。 《安静的位置》...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5069580/#comments">(8回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">11有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5069580_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5069580_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
